Package: RGENERATEPREC
Maintainer: Emanuele Cordano <emanuele.cordano@gmail.com>
License: GPL (>= 2)
Title: Tools to Generate Daily-Precipitation Time Series
Type: Package
Author: Emanuele Cordano
Description: The method 'generate()' is extended for spatial multi-site
    stochastic generation of daily precipitation. It generates precipitation
    occurrence in several sites using logit regression (Generalized Linear
    Models) and D.S. Wilks' approach (Journal of Hydrology, 1998).
Version: 1.2.5
Repository: CRAN
Date: 2019-10-16
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    copula,
    RGENERATE,
    blockmatrix,
    Matrix,
    stringr
Imports:
    RMAWGEN
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown,lubridate,leaflet,lmom,knitcitations,ggplot2,reshape2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/ecor/RGENERATEPREC
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
